          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-1" n="1">You Little scribbling Beau</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-2" n="2">What Demon made you write?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-3" n="3">Because to write you know</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-4" n="4">As much as you can fight.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-5" n="5"><lb/>For Complement so scurvy,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-6" n="6">I wish we had you here,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-7" n="7">We'd turn you topsie Turvy</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-8" n="8">Into a Mug of Beer.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-9" n="9"><lb/>You thought to make a farce on</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-10" n="10">The man, and place we Chose,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-11" n="11">We're sure a single parson</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-12" n="12">Is worth a hundred Beaux.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-13" n="13"><lb/>And you wou'd Make us Vassals</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-14" n="14">Good M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Wig and Wings,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-15" n="15">To silver Clocks and Tassels</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-16" n="16">You wou'd you thing of things.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-17" n="17"><lb/>Because around your Cane</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-18" n="18">A ring of diamonds is set,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-19" n="19">And you in some by Lane</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-20" n="20">Have gain'd a paltry Grisset.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-21" n="21"><lb/>Shall we of sence refin'd</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-22" n="22">Your Trifling Nonsense bear,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-23" n="23">As Noisy as the wind,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-24" n="24">As empty as the Air?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-25" n="25"><lb/>We hate your empty prattle,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-26" n="26">And vow and swear, 'tis true</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-27" n="27">There's more in one child's Rattle,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-427-WILH-line-28" n="28">Than twenty Fops like you──</l>
          </lg>
